%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJonozzo%20said%20outdoor%20walks%20and%20being%20in%20nature%20helped%20her%20stay%20positive%20during%20treatment.%3Cp%3EKatelyn%20Jonozzo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20obstacle%20was%20the%20colostomy%20bag.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20obviously%20super%20self-conscious%20about%20the%20bag%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20But%20as%20she%20started%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20young%20cancer%20patients%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftouchedbycancer.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Gathering%20Place%3C%2Fa%3E%20support%20group%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcolorectalcancer.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EColorectal%20Cancer%20Alliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20began%20to%20embrace%20the%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20go%20to%20the%20pool%20in%20a%20bathing%20suit%2C%20with%20the%20bag%20out%2C%20or%20I%20would%20lift%20my%20shirt%20up%20at%20the%20gym%20and%20let%20people%20know%20that%20the%20bag%20was%20there%2C%20which%20I%20guess%20made%20me%20just%20gain%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20the%20positives%20helped%20her%20keep%20up%20her%20normal%20routine%20as%20much%20as%20she%20could.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20amazing%20that%20they%20found%20out%20how%20to%20pull%20your%20intestine%20out%20and%20you%20could%20still%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20great%20contraption%2C%20if%20you%20ask%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd63d57b-8da9-4e0f-bdd8-a772a4b47432%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe's%20running%20a%20marathon%20with%20her%20cancer%20support%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katelyn%20Jonozzo%20ringing%20cancer%20treatment%20bell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69307c5004d0f0a114f154d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJonozzo%20ringing%20the%20bell%20in%20September%20once%20her%20treatment%20was%20officially%20finished.%3Cp%3EKatelyn%20Jonozzo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20seven%20months%20of%20treatment%2C%20Jonozzo%20was%20deemed%20cancer-free.%20She%20finished%20chemotherapy%20in%20August%20and%20had%20a%20colostomy%20reversal%20in%20November.%20In%20mid-December%2C%20her%20first%20screening%20since%20finishing%20treatment%2C%20she'll%20learn%20more%20about%20her%20future%20screening%20schedule%2C%20which%20she%20already%20knows%20will%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-symptoms-in-my-30s-colonoscopy-cost-insurance-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etwo%20colonoscopies%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe'll%20also%20be%20officially%20cleared%20to%20work%20out%20after%20her%20surgery%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20eager%20to%20go%20back%20to%20her%20old%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20little%20nervous%20just%20because%20normally%20I%20can%20just%20pop%20out%20and%20run%20and%20do%20those%20things%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20take%20baby%20steps%20back%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20plans%20to%20run%20three%20marathons%20in%202026%2C%20with%20the%20hopes%20of%20re-qualifying%20for%20Boston%20through%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20especially%20excited%20for%20the%20Cleveland%20Marathon%20in%20May.%20She'll%20run%20it%20as%20the%20team%20captain%20for%20her%20cancer%20fundraising%20group%2C%20which%20she%20said%20awakened%20new%20passions%20in%20her.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20advocating%2C%20I%20love%20talking%20to%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20always%20loved%20doing%20that%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20didn't%20have%20the%20confidence%20to%20do%20so%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20that%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-cancer-work-career-impact-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecancer%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%20changed%20her%2C%20she%20said%2C%20along%20with%20becoming%20more%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20think%20I'm%20crazy%20for%20saying%20this%2C%20but%20I%20truly%20believe%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20that%20ever%20happened%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20trade%20this%20experience%20for%20anything.%20I%20really%20wouldn't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarathon-runner-stage-3-colon-cancer-no-symptoms-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764846620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69305f0a71107c9f34573f4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarathon-runner-stage-3-colon-cancer-no-symptoms-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Katelyn%20Jonozzo%20lived%20a%20very%20active%20lifestyle%20and%20had%20no%20symptoms%20of%20colon%20cancer%20before%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20at%20stage%203.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarathon-runner-stage-3-colon-cancer-no-symptoms-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20says%20Palestinian%20groups%20returned%20body%20of%20Thai%20hostage%20held%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764846144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fac3f%2Flive%2Fdaf7fe70-d0e1-11f0-8c06-f5d460985095.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcd6x2j4g3z7o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20remains%20of%20agricultural%20worker%20Suthisak%20Rintalak%20were%20recovered%20by%20Hamas%20and%20Palestinian%20Islamic%2