20the%20challenge%20requires%20contestants%20to%20predict%20roughly%2030%20events.%20The%202025%20game%20kicked%20off%20in%20late%202024%2C%20when%20Seif%20sent%20out%20the%20list%20of%20events%20to%20predict%20in%20fields%20such%20as%20politics%2C%20business%2C%20science%2C%20economics%2C%20pop%20culture%2C%20and%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20question%20asked%20the%20contestants%20to%20forecast%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-travis-kelce-engaged-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%20and%20Travis%20Kelce%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20announce%20their%20engagement%20by%20April%201.%20Another%3A%20Would%20Bulgaria%20adopt%20the%20euro%20as%20its%20official%20currency%20on%20or%20before%20July%201%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Leffell%2C%20a%20director%20at%20a%20hedge%20fund%20firm%2C%20was%20filling%20out%20his%20probabilities%20in%20December%20and%20had%20an%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20answering%20the%20questions%2C%20I%20had%20the%20ChatGPT%20screen%20up.%20I%20wondered%2C%20what%20it%20will%20say%20to%20these%20questions%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220cfbc528-72fb-42c8-a03e-d34df7526f87%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20had%20to%20learn%20complex%20rules%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeffell%20reached%20out%20to%20Seif%20to%20ask%20if%20ChatGPT%20could%20take%20part%2C%20and%20Seif%20said%2C%20go%20for%20it.%20So%2C%20Leffell%20got%20started%20by%20pasting%20the%20game's%20rules%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-cloud-service-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einto%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20complex%20rules%2C%20covering%20multiple%20pages.%20Contestants%20must%20assign%20a%20percentage%20based%20on%20the%20likelihood%20of%20each%20event%20happening.%20As%20the%20results%20come%20in%20over%20the%20year%2C%20these%20predictions%20are%20scored%20a%20bit%20like%20golf.%20The%20lowest%20score%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20points%20equal%20to%20the%20square%20of%20the%20difference%20between%20what%20you%20put%20and%20the%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20Seif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20you%20assign%20a%2090%25%20chance%20of%20something%20happening%20and%20you%20get%20it%20right%2C%20you%20get%2010%20points.%20That%20number%20is%20squared%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20total%20of%20100%20points.%20Excellent%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposite%20is%20more%20painful.%20If%20your%2090%25%20probability%20event%20doesn't%20occur%2C%20you%20are%20stuck%20with%20the%20difference%20between%2090%20and%20zero.%20That%2090%20score%20is%20then%20squared%20for%20a%20total%20of%208%2C100%20points.%20Ouch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20only%20the%20scoring%20system.%20There%20are%20whole%20pages%20of%20rules%20on%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20game.%20Leffell%20pasted%20all%20this%20into%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20seconds%20later%2C%20the%20AI%20chatbot%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20providing%20the%20detailed%20rules%20of%20the%20forecasting%20contest.%20Please%20share%20the%20clean%20list%20of%20prompts%20for%20which%20you%20need%20a%20probability%20estimate%2C%20and%20I%20will%20provide%20a%20single%20number%20for%20each%20as%20per%20the%20contest's%20guidelines.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeffell%20pasted%20in%20all%2030%20questions%20at%20once%2C%20and%20ChatGPT%20quickly%20replied%20with%20its%20percentage%20probabilities%20for%20each%20event.%20Leffell%20sent%20those%20to%20Seif%2C%20who%20entered%20the%20responses%20on%20ChatGPT's%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20while%20setting%20this%20machine-prediction%20experiment%20up%2C%20Leffell%20noticed%20something%20intriguing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20one%20question%2C%20related%20to%20an%20NFL%20wild%20card%20outcome%2C%20it%20gave%20a%20mathematical%20response%20that%20was%20statistically%20correct%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20doing%20math%20rather%20than%20qualitative%20stuff.%20That%20was%20notable%20because%20ChatGPT%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20was%20not%20supposed%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-failed-singapore-sixth-grade-exams-psle-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egood%20at%20math%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ea477f5-8acb-4896-a271-c4e6c1cba23b%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20makes%20predictions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%202025%20began%2C%20160%20contestants%20had%20submitted%20their%20predictions%20and%20began%20waiting%20for%20the%20future%20to%20unfurl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20I%20first%20heard%20about%20the%20game%20through%20friends%20of%20mine%20who%20were%20participating.%20One%20is%20a%20hedge%20fund%20manager.%20The%20other%20two%20are%20a%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20and%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20became%20insufferable%20at%20parties%2C%20discussing%20their%20various%20forecasts%2C%20along%20with%20the%20intricacies%20of%20the%20scoring%20system%20and%20other%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20type%20of%20conversation%20that%20bores%20me%20to%20death.%20However%2C%20when%20one%20friend%20mentioned%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-amazon-aws-compute-deal-cloud-ai-adoption-customer-demand-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20was%20taking%20part%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20got%20hooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20a%20machine%20outperform%20160%20humans%20in%20predicting%20all%20these%20events%3F%20AI%20models%20are%20great%20when%20there's%20existing%20data.%20When%20the%20future's%20involved%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20less%20information%20to%20lean%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20recently%20tested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftampon-trade-chatgpt-dan-ives-stock-market-predictions-us-iran-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT's%20stock%20market%20forecasting%20ability%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Could%20it%20excel%20at%20this%20more%20complex%20challenge%2C%20or%20are%20humans%20uniquely%20adept%20at%20foreseeing%20the%20future%20through%20experience%2C%20extrapolation%2C%20and%20intuition%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20year%20progressed%2C%20some%20events%20occurred%2C%20and%20others%20didn't.%20Some%20happened%20too%20late%2C%20while%20others%20developed%20in%20weird%2C%20unexpected%20ways.%20As%20life%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20time%20a%20question%20was%20resolved%2C%20Seif%20updated%20a%20central%20spreadsheet%20and%20sent%20a%20ranking%20to%20all%20the%20contestants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friends%20seized%20on%20every%20update.%20Who%20was%20winning%3F%20Who%20was%20lagging%3F%20And%20most%20of%20all%2C%20where%20was%20ChatGPT%20ranked%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4d41e5f-7684-474d-9556-e8e9bc3314b9%5C%22%3EStrange%20symmetry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20game%20wrapped%20up%20on%20November%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20seven%20years%20we've%20run%20the%20contest%2C%20I%20pulled%20off%20the%20win%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20Seif%20wrote%20in%20his%20final%20email%20update%20of%20the%202025%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20came%2080th%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20we%20had%20160%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrange%20symmetry.%20I%20immediately%20texted%20my%20friends%3A%20This%20means%20ChatGPT%20is%20no%20better%20than%20the%20average%20human!%20Not%20very%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20buddies%2C%20the%20CMO%2C%20replied%3A%20No%2C%20this%20means%20ChatGPT%20is%20as%20good%20as%20the%20average%20human.%20Incredible!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ba9078c-ca3f-4357-ab89-5b833926dcd8%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20missed%20a%20benchmark%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20Seif%20about%20this%2C%20and%20he%20had%20a%20different%20way%20of%20measuring%20ChatGPT's%20predictive%20power%2C%20or%20lack%20thereof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you'd%20put%20a%2050%25%20probability%20for%20each%20event%20happening%2C%20you'd%20have%20gotten%2075%2C000%20points.%20That's%20Seif's%20benchmark%20for%20whether%20contestants%20added%20value%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20got%2082%2C925.%20So%20it%20missed%20that%20benchmark%2C%20essentially%20adding%20negative%20value%2C%20according%20to%20Seif.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20existing%20data%20to%20help%20with%20forecasting%20and%20calculating%20probabilities%2C%20ChatGPT%20did%20better%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20chatbot%20analyzed%20this%20event%20well%2C%20giving%20it%20a%2070%25%20chance%20of%20happening%3A%20%3Cem%3EThe%20winning%20team%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F2025-club-world-cup-photos-empty-stadiums-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFIFA%20Club%20World%20Cup%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20from%20the%20European%20Union%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20performed%20worse%20when%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20data%2C%20or%20it%20missed%20new%20information%20that%20altered%20the%20likelihood%20of%20an%20event%20occurring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20chatbot%20assigned%20a%2095%25%20chance%20of%20this%20happening%3A%20%3Cem%3EAstronauts%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsunita-williams-butch-wilmore-nasa-astronauts-stuck-space-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESuni%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20safely%20return%20to%20Earth%20by%20March%201.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20news%20announcements%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20this%20rescue%20mission%20was%20highly%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20by%20March%201%2C%202025%2C%20Seif%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChatGPT%20just%20wasn't%20up%20with%20the%20news%20on%20that%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ace5e62-df5e-41ff-b3b6-822189aa92b1%5C%22%3EMaybe%20ChatGPT%20