2%3EJulia%20Louis-Dreyfus%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeibovitz%20said%20her%20longtime%20partner%2C%20author%20Susan%20Sontag%2C%20who%20died%20in%202004%2C%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20interested%20in%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20would%20talk%20about%20it%20every%20now%20and%20then%2C%20and%20she%20was%20not%20interested.%20Besides%2C%20we%20didn't%20really%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20relationship.%20We%20had%20two%20separate%20apartments%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20had%20our%20own%20world%2C%20but%20we%20really%20supported%20each%20other%20tremendously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Leibovitz's%20doctor%20told%20her%20she%20still%20had%20that%20option.%20%26quot%3BSo%20he%20said%20to%20me%2C%20'You%20can%20do%20it.'%20I%20said%2C%20'Really%3F'%20And%20I%20did%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20has%20three%20daughters%20who%20are%20now%20in%20their%20twenties.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20kids%20later%20in%20life%20has%20made%20her%20more%20aware%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-parent-lessons-self-care-age-insecurity-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparenting%20as%20an%20older%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStill%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20I'm%20having%20any%20issue%20now%20about%20being%20older%2C%20is%20that%20I%20decided%20to%20have%20them%20older.%20And%20my%20older%20daughter%20gets%20mad%20at%20me%20if%20I%20don't%20take%20care%20of%20myself.%20'Mommy%2C%20I%20want%20you%20to%20live%20longer.'%20And%20you%20worry%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20says%20she%20wants%20to%20continue%20focusing%20on%20her%20career%20and%20give%20her%20daughters%20space%20rather%20than%20hovering%20over%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20not%20necessarily%20being%20so%20smothering%20and%20so%20close%2C%20because%20I%20just%20knew%20I%20was%20an%20older%20mom%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20they%20were%20going%20to%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20me%20leaving%20earlier%20than%20possibly%20being%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20having%20more%20than%20one%20child%20was%20so%20they%20would%20have%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20parenting%2C%20Leibovitz%20says%20aging%20has%20been%20something%20that%20she%20has%20come%20to%20genuinely%20appreciate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20love%20getting%20older.%20You%20kind%20of%20know%20what%20you're%20doing.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20what%20you're%20doing%20is%20good%20or%20better%20or%20whatever.%20It's%20still%20hard%20work%2C%20but%20you%20kind%20of%20know%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20and%20there's%20something%20really%20nice%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn't%20have%20to%20rush%20through%20everything%20anymore%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20things%2C%20I%20think%2C%20naturally%20are%20slowing%20down%2C%20kind%20of%20after%20running%20around%20like%20crazy%2C%20starting%20when%20I%20was%20very%20young.%20And%20so%20it's%20nice%20to%20kind%20of%20slow%20down%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20Leibovitz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeibovitz%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20who%20has%20spoken%20about%20having%20children%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feva-mendes-no-confidence-raise-kids-motherhood-late-geriatric-pregnancy-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEva%20Mendes%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20was%20a%20good%20thing%20she%20waited%20til%20she%20was%2040%20to%20have%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%2020s%2C%20I%20shouldn't%20have%20even%20been%20around%20a%20child.%20I%20was%20foul-mouthed%20and%20smoking.%20I%20definitely%20could%20not%20have%20raised%20kids%20in%20any%20other%20era%20of%20my%20life%20but%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Mendes%20told%20People.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp