vent%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Sciulli%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Team%20One%2C%20Saatchi%20LA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDirector%20Carl%20Erik%20Rinsch%20is%20on%20trial%20in%20NY%2C%20fighting%20charges%20he%20scammed%20Netflix%20out%20of%20%2411%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProsecutors%20say%20Rinsch%20blew%20money%20meant%20for%20his%20sci-fi%20series%20on%20luxuries%20and%20playing%20the%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20jurors%20saw%20how%20he%20lost%20a%20fortune%20on%20options%20trades%20soon%20after%20Netflix%20wired%20the%20cash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDirector%20Carl%20Eric%20Rinsch%20made%20so%20many%20failed%2C%20seven-figure%20option%20bets%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-filmmaker-carl-erik-rinsch-11-million-fraud-trial-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%20wired%20him%20%2411%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20broker%20at%20Wells%20Fargo%20tried%20%E2%80%94%20and%20failed%20%E2%80%94%20to%20stop%20him%2C%20a%20New%20York%20fraud%20jury%20heard%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20afford%20to%20lose%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinsch%20said%2C%20according%20to%20testimony%20by%20his%20former%20Wells%20Fargo%20advisor%2C%20Ronald%20See.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20the%20brokerage%20hit%20the%20brakes%20%E2%80%94%20limiting%20him%20to%20%24250%2C000%20per%20transaction%20%E2%80%94%20the%20show%20developer%20was%20undaunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2030%2C%202019%2C%20just%20three%20weeks%20after%20receiving%20the%20%2411%20million%2C%20Rinsch%20instructed%20See%2C%20of%20Wells%20Fargo%20Advisors%2C%20to%20wire%20his%20remaining%20%248.5%20million%20to%20Citibank%20so%20he%20could%20establish%20a%20new%20brokerage%20account%20with%20Charles%20Schwab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20won't%20put%20restrictions%20on%20me%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinsch%20wrote%20See%20in%20a%20letter%20shown%20to%20jurors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERinsch%2C%2048%2C%20is%20on%20trial%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20fighting%20charges%20that%20he%20had%20no%20right%20to%20use%20the%20%2411%20million%20Netflix%20sent%20him%20on%20anything%20other%20than%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Horse%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20120-minute%20TV%20series%20he'd%20already%20spent%20%2444%20million%20of%20Netflix's%20money%20on.%20(Rinsch%20ultimately%20never%20finished%20a%20single%20episode%20of%20the%20clones-versus-humans%20sci-fi%20thriller.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20lawyers%20counter%20that%20the%20%2411%20million%20was%20actually%20Rinsch's%20contractually-promised%20payment%20for%20having%20completed%20principal%20photography%2C%20and%20was%20his%20money%20to%20spend%20as%20he%20pleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20testimony%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20two%20of%20Rinsch's%20former%20financial%20advisors%20showed%20that%20he%20was%20eager%20to%20spend%20the%20cash%20prosecutors%20say%20the%20director%20had%20quickly%20moved%20into%20his%20Wells%20Fargo%20account.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streamer%20wired%20Rinsch%20the%20%2411%20million%20on%20March%206%2C%202020%2C%20as%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20halted%20film%20production%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20weeks%2C%20he%20then%20lost%20some%20%245.8%20million%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20it%20on%20highly%20risky%20options%20trades%20involving%20Gilead%20Sciences%2C%20which%20was%20developing%20COVID-19%20treatment%20drugs.%20(See%20would%20earn%20a%20%2422%2C000%20fee%20on%20these%20losses%2C%20the%20defense%20pointed%20out%20on%20cross-examination.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20was%20off%20to%20the%20races%20again%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20switched%20to%20Charles%20Schwab%2C%20according%20to%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20send%20%243%20mm%20personal%20to%20get%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20to%20his%20new%20financial%20advisor%2C%20Adam%20Checchi%2C%20who%20also%20testified%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understood%20that%20to%20mean%20three%20million%20from%20his%20personal%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20Checchi%20said%20under%20questioning%20by%20a%20federal%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChecchi%20told%20jurors%20that%20Rinsch%20would%20soon%20lose%20almost%20%246%20million%20more%2C%20mostly%20on%20failed%2C%20highly%20risky%20bets%20that%20Gilead's%20stock%20would%20rise%20and%20that%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20a%20broad%2C%20diversify%20kind%20of%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinsch%20explained%20in%20a%20late%20March%202020%20email%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20pursues%20%26quot%3Baggressive%26quot%3B%20option%20trading%20%26quot%3Bfully%20expecting%20to%20lose%20it%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-peter-friedlander-testifies-director-carl-rinsch-fruad-trial-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eformer%20Netflix%20executive%20Peter%20Friedlander%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20on%20Monday%20called%20Rinch's%20project%20%26quot%3Bvisionary%2C%26quot%3B%20completed%20a%20second%20day%20of%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20overhead%20screens%2C%20defense%20attorney%20Benjamin%20Zeman%20showed%20Friedlander%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20jury%20%E2%80%94%20emails%20from%20August%202019%2C%20in%20which%20Rinsch%20begged%20for%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20support%26quot%3B%20with%20casting%20in%20Brazil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShow%20is%20set%20to%20collapse%2C%26quot%3B%20Rinsch%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20is%20blaming%20the%20implosion%20of%20White%20Horse%20on%20Netflix's%20decision%20to%20pull%20support%20for%20the%20project%20in%20September%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20email%20chain%20projected%20throughout%20the%20courtroom%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Zeman%20attempted%20to%20show%20jurors%20that%20a%20year%20earlier%2C%20Friedlander%20was%20already%20cold%20toward%20the%20show%20developer's%20requests%20for%20help.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26qu